e616210516f4e3b2f0c6297?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ankitdandhare\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ankitdandhare</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 27, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Simple, easy, useful and effective. Really amazing plugin, one click and its done.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">cumple con lo que se necesita</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/marcoaf20\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e8441608080f18e06969658638ec9a9b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e8441608080f18e06969658638ec9a9b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/marcoaf20\" class=\"reviewer-name\">marcoaf20</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 26, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Hace los 301 redirect bien, aunque no vi que los hiciera en el .htaccess, no se que tan bueno o malo sea eso pero me salvó ahora que hice migración de página</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">It does helpful stuff in the background</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nor3ert\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5bd54f3699414436946551598533dd2d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5bd54f3699414436946551598533dd2d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nor3ert\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Norbert <small>(nor3ert)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 25, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Who knew that old links to a previous website can be utilized feeding traffic to your new one. Genious.\nI never thought that this could/should be done. So glad I heard about it.\nLike the import feature once I figured it out.\nThank you.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Simply works.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><